ane france humanitarian award presented by nationwide recognizing outstanding charitable and volunteer efforts of nascar fans was created in her honor in france was a longtime community leader in daytona beach and best known as a steadfast champion of health care for children she assisted in the establishment of the “speediatrics” children’s care unit at halifax health in daytona beach and at homestead hospital in homestead floridain  france was presented the halifax medical center foundation’s humanitarian award in recognition of her advocacy commitment support and advancement of numerous area community service organizations including the volusiaflagler chapter of the american red crossshe was a member of the junior league of daytona beach serving on the boards of numerous area community service organizationsin july  she was named as an honorary cochairperson for the childress institute for pediatric trauma a project headed by longtime nascar team owner richard childress in winstonsalem“we are saddened by the passing of my mother and inspiration betty jane france lesa france kennedy said in a statement released by isc she played a significant role in nascar’s history leading the charge to elevate the experience of our sport for the fans who love it and her philanthropic efforts will forever remain a part of our sport“my mother launched the nascar foundation as a steadfast champion of children’s healthcare and in  the betty jane france humanitarian award was created in her honor in her hometown of daytona beach she served as a community leader touching countless lives with her charitable efforts she was very touched and proud last year when halifax health medical center unveiled a statue just outside the hospital tower which also bears our family’s name“beyond her greatest community service her starring role was that of mother to my brother brian and me she was an incredible role model cherished friend and someone who demonstrated limitless possibilities that helped so many people pursue their dreams“her legacy will be treasured and she will forever be missed not only by her loving family and close friends but by the many lives she touched along the way”funeral arrangements are pending betty jane france was an awesome lady always charitable a true advisor over the years to bill jr during major growth in our sport rip— dale earnhardt jr dalejr august   our sport lost another great woman today betty jane france will be missed— tony stewart tonystewart august   thoughts  prayers with the france family today betty jane france helped make the sport what it is today  impacted many w her foundation— joey logano joeylogano august   thinking of the france family this morning chandrajanway and i loved visiting with betty jane we will deeply miss hernascar— jimmie johnson jimmiejohnson august   very sad to hear of betty janes passing she did so much for our sport  for others thinking of the france family httpstcoumdegsewd— jeff gordon jeffgordonweb august   read this next nascar sprint cup disappointed chase elliott comes up just short in nascar pure michigan  nascar earthcam see bristol motor speedway transform into a seat football stadium racing nascar’s king speaks richard petty on danica donald trump brian france and more nascar sprint cup kyle larson and chevrolet win nascar sprint cup race at michigan see morenascar share facebook tweet pinterest email related stories nascar opinion indianapolis nascar xfinity race has brickyard  implications nascar arca notebook chad finley falls short dalton sargeant back the title mix nascar dalton sargeant was lucky and good in lucas oil indianapolis arca triumph nascar kyle busch had indy  deal done but was denied by nascar team owner nascar nascar mulling additional limits for cup drivers in trucks xfinity story topics racing nascar follow usfacebooktwitterinstagrampinterestget more autoweekmagazinecar news reviews motorsports auto shows and stunning photography delivered right to your mailbo