east  million will be eligible for varying reductions in a  percent buyer’s premium to be added to the highest bid visit platinumluxuryauctionscom for details“we do most of our screening afterward” mathias lenssen product manager for the auction said of the daily preview visitors “we want to know who will be in the room on saturday who our bidders will be but anybody can come no appointment necessary”that includes a modestly paid newspaper reporter who received a tour from the frances’ longtime personal assistant dana sunshine on a recent afternoon no photos allowed“all the decorating ideas came from their travels around the world” said sunshine  striding across the enormous blackandwhite spanish marble checkerboard floor in the footlong foyer home to a gleaming black kawai grand piano equipped with a system to automatically play along with cds inserted into a player beneath the keyslike all the furniture and accessories that remain it comes with the housethe foyer is the connection from the home’s entrance accented by grand dual staircases to the river room with its picture windows on the intracoastal waterwaya bar in the river room was modeled on the one in the beverly wilshire hotel in beverly hills calif sunshine said across the room an imposing armoire — customized to hold a flatscreen tv — was shipped from new orleans where france found it in an antique store on a table bronze statues depict a boy and a girl hunched over a storybook a nod to betty janes interest in childrens causes nearby betty jane’s home office is lined with builtin bookshelves where titles reflect other wideranging interestsbooks on art history california wines and earth science share space with literature anthologies poetry collections birding “venetian palaces” and “the hillier gardener’s guide to trees  shrubs”that interest in landscaping is evident in the manicured grounds of the  feet of private frontage on the halifax including a foot dock capable of accommodating several deepwater vessels two covered lanais offer large entertainment areas with fireplaces that look more like something from a european cafea fountain imported from italy is the dominant feature against a backdrop of magnolias oaks weeping willows oleanders bougainvilleas and fragrant confederate jasmine“she had pictures of window treatments shapes marble gardens” sunshine said “everywhere she went she took pictures they built the house to entertain”befitting its name the river room also offers postcardworthy views of the halifax through roomlength picture windows equipped with electronic shades to shield the sunupstairs there’s an equally lovely river view from a master suite equipped with a grand vestibule sitting area separate ensuite baths adorned in custom tiles and wood as well as separate roomsized his and her dressing areas a breakfast kitchen in the master suite leads to an oversized balcony where betty jane france used to enjoy reclining on a day bed to watch the activity on the river sunshine saidthere’s different décor in each of the estate’s five full bathrooms and six halfbaths sunshine saidthat includes green pakistan onyx in bill france’s master bath crosscut honey onyx in his wife’s master bath to intricately designed rosette patterns in other ornamental light fixtures a wall of betty jane’s dressing area is occupied by custom cabinets to hold her shoes each illuminated and equipped with glass windows on another wall was a cedar closet for furs“i think she almost had it decorated before the house was finished” sunshine said “she knew what she wanted and she was detailed” subscribe today choose the plan that’s right for you digital access or digital and print delivery learn more nascar executive vice president betty jane france passes away  fox sports menu fox sports scores nascar executive vice president betty jane france passes away betty jane france speaks during the betty jane france humanitarian award reception inside wynn las vegas during nascar champions week on december   sarah crabillnascar via getty images foxsports aug   at a et shares nascar’s founding family has lost one of its most cherished leaders with the passing of betty jane france the executive vice president and assistant treasurer of nascar and chairperson of the nascar foundation born betty jane zachary in winstonsalem nc france met her husband nascar chairman and ceo william c france better known as bill france jr in her hometown they married and relocated to daytona beach florida bill france jr passed away in june  tweets remembering nascars betty jane france betty jane was the mother of lesa france kennedy ceo of international speedway corp and nascar chairman and ceo brian france “last night the nascar family lost a mother a grandmother a friend and the light that guided the sport’s charitable arm” said brian france “my mother taught us incredible values that of love patience compassion and joy she embraced life every day and nothing fueled her passion more than children her unmatched efforts in building the nascar foundation improved the lives of millions of children throughout this country and because of that her legacy will live forever  “my father leaned on my mother throughout his life relying on her wisdom and calming demeanor to help grow the sport of nascar she was there every step of the way when we lost my father her positive presence remained as she used her immense skill to grow nascar’s heart and soul the nascar foundation latest from nascar alex bowman to replace dale earnhardt jr in the no denny hamlin wins to end the losing streak for jgr   loudonrichard petty on with jeff hammond  nascar race hubwatch jordan taylor clip tommy milner send no  corvette hard into the tire barrier  canadian tire martin truex jr dominates in overtime in kentucky as kenseth and dillon wreck behind him my mother was a special woman and an impressive person and she will be dearly missed” a longtime community leader in daytona beach betty jane was best known as a steadfast champion of health care for children she assisted in establishing of the speediatrics children’s care unit at halifax health in daytona beach and was also instrumental in the establishment of a similar unit at homestead hospital homestead florida she was the driving force in fundraising and design of these units she was a member of the junior league of daytona beach and served on boards of numerous area community service organizations including the volusiaflagler chapter of the american red cross and the garden club of halifax county in  betty jane was presented the halifax medical center foundation’s humanitarian award in recognition of her advocacy commitment support and advancement of health care and human services for women infants children and families france became chairwoman of the nascar foundation upon the foundation’s inception in  the foundation based in daytona beach fla is a  nonprofit entity that embodies the compassion of the nascar family and its commitment to serving communities the foundation’s flagship charitable initiative the annual nascar day held each may has benefited a variety of causes including speediatrics in july  she was named as an honorary cochairperson for the childress institute for pediatric trauma a project headed by longtime nascar team owner richard childress in winston salem nc the betty jane france humanitarian award was created in her honor in  through the nascar foundation this award recognizes outstanding charitable and volunteer efforts of nascar fans she presented this award annually at the nascar awards banquet fox fantasy auto form a racing team compete for prizes play now monstertomjensentruckxfinity shares fox sports go live now fs a et big basketball  philadelphia fs p et road to the octagon  weidman vs gastelum featured fox today p et ufc fight night  prelims weidman vs gastelum fox today p et ufc fight night  weidman vs gastelum fs today p et cardinals at cubs upcoming fs today p et golf  us junior am